
Overview of noun loon

The noun loon has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                           
1. (1) loon -- (a worthless lazy fellow)
2. (1) loon, diver -- (large somewhat primitive fish-eating diving bird of the northern hemisphere having webbed feet placed far back; related to the grebes)
3. addle-head, addlehead, loon, birdbrain -- (a person with confused ideas; incapable of serious thought)
